  "prompt": "What's the average number of answers to each question on Quora?",
  "response": "The average number of answers to each question on Quora can vary widely depending on the topic, popularity of the question, and the community's engagement. While there isn't a specific, readily available average number of answers, some questions may receive only a few answers, while others can gather hundreds or even thousands. The variation makes it challenging to provide a precise average without comprehensive data analysis. Generally, more popular or trending questions tend to have more answers, while niche or less commonly discussed topics may have fewer responses.",
